data.description: Location! Location! Location! Welcome to 38745 Desert View Dr. Palmdale!  This property is located in the west side of the city of Palmdale. It features 3 Bedrooms and 2 full baths. Established neighborhood! It has potentials opportunities.  House is located in cul-de-sac, extra-large drive, covered patio, paved and close to mall, shopping, church, hospitals, schools, and the 14 freeway, commuter friendly. Needs ''loving tender care'' TLC. First-time buyers, growing families, and investors looking for attractive housing options.
